21001.name: Tunnel of Sticks - Entrance
21001.description:
A narrow shaft from above opens into a tangled cavern of braced sticks.
The maze stretches into darkness. Darkness clings to every surface. The
stone walls press close, cold and damp.

21002.name: Tunnel of Sticks
21002.description:
Twisted roots and splintered timbers brace the earthen walls, forming a
claustrophobic maze of sticks and shadow. The air is damp and still. The
silence is oppressive and watchful. Darkness clings to every surface.
